.Dd $Mdocdate: August 27 2018 $
.Dt HIDWUSB 4
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm hidwusb
.Nd HiSilicon USB 3.0 glue logic
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Cd "hidwusb* at fdt?"
.Cd "xhci* at fdt?"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
driver controls the interface logic for the Synopsys DesignWare USB
3.0 controller on HiSilicon SoCs.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr intro 4 ,
.Xr xhci 4
.Sh HISTORY
The
.Nm
device driver first appeared in
.Ox 6.4 .
